{"tid":494121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"趁開放日校外派傳單遭警圍 聖母書院學生批校方「多餘」","createTime":"2017-12-09T09:26:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T15:15:59.000Z","uid":28366,"like":123,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"e0d7d7523c8db1021a4c06ff193c3c047ab34ed2","tid":494121,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:26:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/09/172119_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F09%2F172119_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5e3763cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聖母書院本土關注組成員早前在校內張貼與本土有關的傳單及海報，至少3名學生需要面臨校內紀律處分。關注組成員再趁學校開放日到門外派傳單，但未派發已被便衣警察「包圍」，有成員被警員抄下身份證號，關注組發言人懷疑是校方報警。<br />\n<br />\n聖母書院本土關注組夥同學生動源、香港民族陣線等團體，趁學校開放日到校外派傳單，批評校方干預學生討論「2047何去何從」等本土議題的言論自由。但活動開始前已有警車停泊在附近明，且不斷有軍裝警員巡邏。當關注組和學生動源的成員聚集後，隨即有5名便衣警員上前命令參與者出示身份證，並抄下他們的個人資料，其後亦有多名便衣警員在校外不同位置監視。<br />\n<br />\n聖母本土關注組發言人張希婷指，今次行動是為顯示香港人有表達自由，批評校方早前不斷打壓學生討論本土議題，如沒收「香港這個地方還能表達自由」的傳單，更新增了校規，禁止學生在校內派傳單。讀中四的張希婷指，自從他們進行一連串行動後，在校內已被針對，「成日畀校方召見、每個星期都叫你傾偈」。她更指，另一位成員謝穎妍今日被校方禁止踏出校門，令她無法參與派傳單。<br />\n<br />\n張稱活動開前校外已有大批警員聚集，質疑是校方報警，認為校方的舉動「多餘」，明顯因本土和港獨議題變成驚弓之鳥，「有好多人（喺校外）派傳單，同本土無關，又唔見佢哋有事？」。《蘋果》就校方有否報警向聖母書院查詢，但職員只稱今日是學校開放日，拒絕回應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/09/172152_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F09%2F172152_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7973511a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">聖母書院本土關注組趁學校開放日在校門外派傳單。 （謝榮耀攝）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/09/172158_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F09%2F172158_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5f55ea15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">圖為在場監視的便衣警員。 （廖梓霖攝）(蘋果日報)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/09/172201_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F09%2F172201_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1b426020&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">同場亦有學生動源及香港民族陣線成員參與。（謝榮耀攝）(蘋果日報)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/09/172204_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F09%2F172204_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e5e9be87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">聖母書院開放日。 （謝榮耀攝）(蘋果日報)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/09/172208_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F09%2F172208_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=de2d6c8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">學生向途人派發傳單。（謝榮耀攝）(蘋果日報)</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171209/57560270\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171209%2F57560270&d=Cm8rMD9sWM3SSTfCICCbrMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=12f76c4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171209%2F57560270&h=16c47918\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171209/57560270</a>"},{"pid":"6acbac990a569139cd33fb00a5c651c638b56582","tid":494121,"uid":28366,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T09:32:53.000Z","msg":"勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid